author: Eric Campbell And Lisa McGregor
title: Singapore has been held up as a model in the coronavirus fight. Here's five strategies it is using
description: Before Singapore had even confirmed its first COVID-19 case, it already had a testing regime in place. But despite the nation's initial success, experts are asking if it can hold covonavirus at bay indefinitely.
